ophene over bilayer MoS2 in terms of\nstiffness and compliance. Our results can pave the way for future studies on\nbilayer borophene structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 11:09:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
