nel for $A$. The function $W$ allows you\nto define an spectral projection in the linear space of the main eigenfunction\nof the Ruelle operator for $A$.\n  Given $A$, we describe explicit expressions for $W$ and the dual potential\n$A^*$, for $A$ in a family of functions introduced by P. Walters. We present\nconditions for $A$ to be symmetric and to be of twist type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 11:34:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
