ayNet-trained models are\nmore robust and thus the preferred choice for general-purpose document-layout\nanalysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 14:25:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-18"}
