AN formulations\nis heavy-tailed and show that clipping improves the performance of SEG/SGDA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 15:21:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 07:51:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-02"}
